  <entry>
    <title>人生与铅笔</title>
    <url>/2023/03/06/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8E%E9%93%85%E7%AC%94/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>人生就像铅笔，刚开始很尖，但慢慢地就被磨得圆滑了。<br>不过，等到太过圆滑时，就差不多又该挨削了。</p>
]]></content>
