  <entry>
    <title>岸上枝叶</title>
    <url>/2023/02/10/%E5%B2%B8%E4%B8%8A%E6%9E%9D%E5%8F%B6/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>立命安身处处家，<br>幽香碧绿漫天涯。<br>披星戴雨引朝露，<br>栉风沐雨染夕霞。<br>一岁一枯无恨意，<br>一颦一笑自芳华。<br>位卑不忘立风骨，<br>来世依然不羡花。</p>
]]></content>
